25:43.680 --> 25:44.940
Hati-hati, Cikgu Liu.

25:46.680 --> 25:47.540
Xiong Yuanbao.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.040
Mu Qingyun.

25:50.200 --> 25:52.000
Datang ke pejabat saya sekejap.

